Update container plugin from 0.6.1 to 0.6.4 to fix GHSA-78h2-9frx-2jm8 and GHSA-fcv2-xgw5-pqxf

The container plugin v0.6.4 bumps github.com/go-jose/go-jose/v4 from v4.1.3
(vulnerable) to v4.1.4 (fixed), which resolves GHSA-78h2-9frx-2jm8 (Go JOSE
panics in JWE decryption).

v0.6.4 also includes the v0.6.3 update to github.com/sigstore/sigstore from
v1.9.5 to v1.10.4, resolving GHSA-fcv2-xgw5-pqxf (path traversal in sigstore
legacy TUF client).

